('d0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000012', 'JOB', 'Working Student Brand (m|w|d)', 'Working Student Brand (m|w|d) at idealo internet GmbH.', ARRAY['Marketing and pr','college coursework completed'], '{"external_id": "public-job-00036", "requirements_text": "Ideas only become visible when they are executed. This is exactly where you contribute - by combining data, creativity, and structured execution to shape how idealo is perceived in the German market. Within the Brand Team, you actively support how campaigns are developed and brought to life. You collaborate across different functions and contribute your own ideas that quickly become tangible. About your new role You support the Brand Team in executing and developing brand projects in Germany. You take on clearly defined tasks as well as smaller projects end-to-end. Your work connects analysis, creative thinking, and reliable execution. When a campaign goes live and everything runs smoothly, you see the direct outcome of your work. Your responsibilities You analyze brand tracking data and derive concrete insights for campaigns and brand initiatives You prepare reports in a structured way and make results accessible and usable for stakeholders You support the execution of brand projects, for example campaign assets or merchandise initiatives You research trends and cultural developments in the German market and translate them into relevant input You independently execute smaller projects, such as landing pages or campaign components Skills &amp; Requirements You are enrolled at a university and have at least one year of studies remaining You work in a structured way and deliver tasks reliably and with attention to detail You have an interest in data analysis, research, and translating insights into actions You have a strong sense for brands, trends, and cultural developments You take ownership and independently drive topics forward. You enjoy tackling challenges actively and solving them pragmatically. d use data and reasoning to debate ideas\u2014then fully commit once a deci", "skills_required": ["Marketing and pr", "college coursework completed"], "work_mode": "REMOTE", "employment_type": "EMPLOYED", "external_url": "https://www.arbeitnow.com/jobs/companies/idealo-internet-gmbh/working-student-brand-mwd-berlin-464956"}'::jsonb, 'US', true, '[0.00821969,-0.05166997,-0.01174979,-0.04468998,0.05848980,-0.08014052,0.02834955,-0.00408146,-0.01100930,-0.01947353,0.02091116,-0.01476533,0.01042147,-0.01333525,-0.04701155,0.03701179,-0.09698939,0.07885726,-0.01392337,0.05944043,-0.03051480,-0.01156153,-0.05831594,0.05610373,-0.04016437,-0.00831635,-0.00536189,0.04309549,0.05903401,-0.02079818,-0.03168312,0.01477720,0.00151703,-0.02730758,0.00351706,-0.01631944,-0.02692586,-0.02226869,-0.04076278,0.08763231,-0.01386937,0.01486871,0.06116168,0.04545925,0.06025597,-0.02180569,-0.02953405,-0.01034918,0.01819210,0.03361910,-0.02887835,-0.01888169,-0.05401910,-0.02856659,0.02015399,0.02993746,-0.03154978,0.00177942,-0.02093235,-0.00292604,-0.08009201,0.05134282,-0.05802323,0.06684952,-0.01041683,0.00771016,0.04801835,0.03114548,-0.03961267,-0.00332322,-0.02540173,-0.03808552,0.00206211,0.04446782,0.00625167,0.00999690,-0.03113000,-0.06593334,-0.00067150,0.00479491,0.00752376,0.02806052,0.05047292,-0.00349967,-0.00690886,-0.00213785,0.01968042,-0.03418486,-0.00384437,0.01885340,-0.00046078,0.04622646,-0.01373582,-0.00880050,-0.00217633,-0.01093450,0.04352022,0.02017845,0.01309513,-0.01752650,0.01099372,-0.02081846,0.00865395,-0.01022870,-0.01866183,0.02114329,-0.08137030,-0.03766488,-0.03336559,-0.03261021,0.00806681,-0.02169279,0.06817325,0.00370449,0.02442489,0.05507876,-0.04724716,-0.00759181,0.03565638,-0.00036838,0.04067120,-0.01414420,-0.01203129,0.02017613,-0.05691823,0.01204737,-0.00342935,-0.01299322,0.03840670,0.00450941,0.00404653,0.03206775,-0.02994269,-0.01545072,0.00549839,-0.02261051,0.00610994,0.02669582,0.05134725,0.00126062,-0.03291087,-0.02787925,-0.01505262,-0.03717361,-